Files.Description: Windows Driver Kit Version 7.1.0 (x86, x64, and ia64) - DVD (English)
Files.Notes:

This version of the WDK is an update of the WDK 7.0.0 and contains the headers, libraries, build tools, build environments, code samples, documentation, and other tools that software developers use to create drivers and kernel software for the following operating systems:

  • Windows 7
  • Windows Vista
  • Windows XP
  • Windows Server 2008 R2
  • Windows Server 2008
  • Windows Server 2003
